<div class="title">Light Me Up</div>
<div class="substance">2C-I & Cannabis (with Salvia divinorum?)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Demotriton&Exact=1">Demotriton</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Demotriton. "Light Me Up: An Experience with 2C-I & Cannabis (with Salvia divinorum?) (exp39356)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 20, 2005. erowid.org/exp/39356</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
